Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.32,0:00:06.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}てめぇが売ったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.32,0:00:06.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How many are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.32,0:00:08.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ウボォーを！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.32,0:00:08.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Around five thousand. And that's a fifth of what they were expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:17.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}イエスと　とるぜ！ どけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:17.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No... Apparently, he's been playing games in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:22.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}話!?　何もねえな！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:22.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's so obsessed with Gungi, \Nhe's been skipping meals. Then what about all this food?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:25.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}落ち着きなよ これは　予言だから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:25.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Should we take it for ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:28.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}行動によっては　回避もできるって 団長が言っただろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:28.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You want to take on the King \Nand his Royal Guard? Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:32.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ヒソカ　今週 何があったか説明しろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:32.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.29,0:00:35.36,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}言えない。 あぁん？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.29,0:00:35.36,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Sometimes, you can't see how strong someone \Nis until you have enough strength yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:40.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　そこにある １つ目の詩の内容は事実だった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:40.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They're monsters. I'll do as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:46.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}…とだけ言っておこう。 聞いたろ　どけ！ まぁ　待てって。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:46.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When Shaia-dono gave us our powers, he'd probably anticipated that \Nthings would turn out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.31,0:00:48.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ヒソカ　なぜ　言えない？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.31,0:00:48.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hagya's the only one who doesn't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:52.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それを言ったら 言えない内容を言ったも同然。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:52.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you call him by his old name, he gets mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:39.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ヒソカの占いから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:39.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Like the others, he has used \Nonly physical attacks thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:44.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}彼が裏切り者だと疑った ノブナガが　刀を抜いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:44.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, let me know if he shows his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:55.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}チッ　やめとくぜ。 てめぇは　やりづれぇからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:55.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once Welfin and Brovada arrive, \Nwe'll take care of those figures in white. I can also check out the \Npowers those two have.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:03.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん？ 何!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:03.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn, I lost sight of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:08.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ノブナガ。 少し黙れ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:08.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Leol-sama, it appears that the suit \Nwith glasses is able to teleport.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:14.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今の　団長か？ 多分。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:14.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Knov's ability is called Hide and Seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:18.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ヒソカ　いくつか質問する。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:18.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Four-Dimensional Apartment Complex \NHide and Seek It allows him to teleport.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:25.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}答えられないものは 「言えない」でいい。 詩にあった　「攫われた秘密」 というのは　何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:25.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}By placing a hand against a wall or the ground, \Nhe can open a portal to access Nen space.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:29.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}団員の能力。 それは　何人だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:29.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He is able to transport people \Nand objects through that portal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:35.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}７人…　いや　８人か。 団長に　ウボォーギン
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:35.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hide and Seek creates a Nen space of \Ntwenty-one rooms, on four floors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:40.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}シズク　マチ　フランクリン パクノダ　シャルナークに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:40.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Each room is isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:48.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}僕で　８人だ。 ん？　お前が　コルトピの能力を 知ったのは　昨日か。 その通り。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:48.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The entrance shuts when anyone enters, so to return to the real world, \None must exit by a different door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:52.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}相手の能力は？ 言えない。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:52.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It is possible to create multiple entrances.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:55.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}相手の　なりかたちは？ 言えない。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:55.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The number of possible entrances differs \Ndepending on the size of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:59.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前と相手との関係は？ 言えない。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:59.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The exit leads back to the portal used for entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:03.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なるほど。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:03.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So, as a general rule, one can only enter \Nand exit via the location of the entry portal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:16.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「赤目の客」　鎖野郎は 最低でも２つの能力を有する敵だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:16.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}However, using Knov's master key, an exit can be linked to any portal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:28.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}後者の能力は　「掟の剣」という 表現から察するところ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:28.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Nothing out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:32.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}相手に　何らかのルールを 強いるものだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:32.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Still quiet on the battlefront.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:34.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「俺にウソをつくな」と
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:34.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Morel's Deep Purple is used for \Nprimarily defensive purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:39.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「俺に関する説明を一切するな」 といったところか。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:39.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If a puppet encounters someone who \Nisn't an ally, it will keep its distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:43.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ここからは　さらに想像によるが ヒソカの体内には
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:43.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If it comes under attack, it will \Nretreat, while fighting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:46.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}敵が仕掛けた何かが 埋まっている。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:46.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The puppets fight back by throwing \Nnearby objects at the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:59.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「物々交換」で「差し出す」と あるにもかかわらず 「攫う」のでは 前後の文章が食い違ってしまう。 これは　「掟の剣」が ヒソカを攻撃するという予言を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:59.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They avoid direct contact, so the enemy won't realize \Nthey are Nen puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:03.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}暗示させるため。 つまり　「差し出す」には
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:03.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's a Chimera...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:10.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「剣で刺す」という意味も 掛けてある。 あぁ…　いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:10.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What is it doing? We're pretty far from the battlefield. Is it scouting the area?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:15.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ヒソカの言動を規制している剣は かなり強制力の大きな能力だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:15.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There were strange dragonflies around town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:19.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やっぱり　いいよ　あなたは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:19.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I thought they were a local species, \Nbut might they be created from his Nen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:23.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}絶対に　あなたは　僕が殺る
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:23.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's very likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:28.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ちょっと　整理してみましょう。 敵は　鎖の使い手。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:28.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If it's a Chimera Ant that specializes in \Ngathering intel, I must neutralize it quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:32.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}操作系なら　実物の鎖を使って ウボォーを倒した。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:32.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The battle is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:38.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}具現化系なら　「念」で作った鎖を 使って　ウボォーを倒した。 それって　何か違いあるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:38.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:43.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}大ありさ　具現化系なら 手ぶらを装うことができる。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:43.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Aren't you gonna touch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:49.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これは　大きなメリットだよ。 そっか　具現化系は イメージ修行が大変だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:49.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Look how close I am... I know you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:53.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一度　具現化ができてしまえば 出し入れ自由だもんね。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:53.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Whoa, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:56.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}問題は　それより ヒソカを縛っている力。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:56.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I knew you were faking it. You can't trick me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何かを守らせてんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}With you being so noisy, I can't fall asleep! Give me some peace and quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:04.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}２つの命令である可能性は高い。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:04.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あとは 鎖野郎への攻撃不可とかね。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I won't let you get any sleep! I'll keep making noise until you chase me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:15.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そして　多分　約束を破ったら死ぬ。 フフフフ　愉快だね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:15.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Idiot... If that's what you wanted, \Nyou should have set a rule to force people to keep chasing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:19.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}僕の体内に「掟の剣」なんて 刺さってないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:19.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Looks like he's still getting \Nused to his new power...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:23.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あの予言は　僕の創作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:23.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Have it your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:28.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}能力を話した人数も ８人じゃなく２人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:28.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I won't be getting up for the next five hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:31.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もしも　団長が 僕の暗示に気づかなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:31.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's really focused on making \Nthis a contest of speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:40.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「旅団」全員を敵に回す 危険な賭け 全ては　「クモ」を ヨークシンにとどまらせ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:40.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Coupled with his constant need for attention, it's unlikely that he'll settle for \Nany other type of contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:43.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}団長と戦うため
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:43.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm not gonna let you sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:46.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ヨークシンを出れば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:46.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:49.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いつ　また団長に会えるか 分からないからね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:49.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm within reach... Get up! Look how close I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:56.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}２つ目のヒソカの予言は どういう意味なのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:56.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If he gives up and moves away...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:26.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なるほど。 ウボォー　ヒソカ　シズク
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:26.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}9-9-1, marshal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:30.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}パクノダ　シャルナーク 半分まで　あと１人。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:30.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}1-5-1, marshal. 7-9-1, pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:34.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}他には　死の予言が出た者は いないんだな？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:34.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}2-3-1, pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:37.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}じゃあ　俺かフェイタンか コルトピだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:37.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}8-1-1, spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:43.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達　データ不足で 占ってもらえてねえから。 僕は　ここに残るよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:43.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}2-3-1, cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:47.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}死ぬ前に　まだ やりたいことが　あるんでね。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:47.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}9-1-1, fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}仮宿は離れない。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}2-7-2, musketeer. The marshal has been isolated...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:56.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}団長　どうする？ 引くか　残るか。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:56.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll call this "remote concealment."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:08.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}残ろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:08.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}3-2-2, major general.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:11.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ダメだ。 えっ　何で？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:11.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さっきまで 「幻影旅団」を捕まえるって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Her initial placement was exactly as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:18.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ノリノリだったじゃん。 捕まえても 意味なくなったからだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:18.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}She's shifting toward my marshal \Nwithout breaking her crane formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:22.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だから　何でさ？ 「旅団」に懸けられてた賞金が パになったんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:22.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let us begin, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:24.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}残ってんのは　リスクだけだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:24.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Her first move will be to position \Nher archer on her right flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:27.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そりゃそうだけど 「旅団」を捕まえること自体は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:27.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}She'll probably try a three-pronged \Nattack to end it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:35.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}無意味じゃないよ！ そういうの 趣旨が変わるっていうんだよ。 俺達が　ここへ来た最初の目的 忘れたのかよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:35.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But shifting her pieces to the right \Nexposes her left flank to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:38.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}『グリードアイランド』。 だろうが！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:38.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's time to disrupt your rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:44.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}少しでも金策に走んないで どうすんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:44.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}1-9-3, new archer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:47.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}実はさ　俺　ゲームに関しては 秘策があるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:47.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:51.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何だよ　秘策って。 ん…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:51.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}9-7-1, new spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:53.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今は　まだ内緒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:53.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}2-9-1, knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:56.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}てめぇ　もったいぶらずに言えよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:56.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Her three-pronged attack \Nand left flank movement
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:59.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}絞まるって　ホントに絞まってる！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:59.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}will cost me two pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:02.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}とにかく　ゲームは俺に任せて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:02.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But that created an opening in her left flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:08.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう少し「旅団」のほうを 追ってみようよ。 本当に秘策は　あるんだろうな。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:08.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}She'll probably expect me to \Ngo all-in from that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:12.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　絶対に うまく行くってわけじゃないけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:12.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But I won't! Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:18.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前の読みでは　何％ぐらいだ？ え？ その作戦が成功する確率だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:18.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}5-5-1, lieutenant general.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:30.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ　いや…　やっぱり ６０％ってとこかな。 恐らく　五分五分ってとこか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:30.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Each of her moves has followed \Na set rhythm until just now, when she froze.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:33.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それでも ２日で６０億稼ぐよりか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:33.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Given the current placement, I can attack through the \Ncenter in unlimited ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:36.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よっぽど　現実的な数字だな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:36.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There is no best move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:40.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よし　分かった ゲームの件は　とりあえず任す。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:40.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}With every turn, I have the \Nability to extend the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:43.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そのかし　「旅団」のほうは 俺達だけじゃ　絶対無理だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:43.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now, let me hear you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:47.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカの協力が 絶対必要条件だからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:47.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}squeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:11.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}緋の眼の番も頼むわよ。 ああ　こいつらがいるから 大丈夫だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:11.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}9-2-1, new lieutenant general.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:32.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうだった？ 何とも要領を得ないな。 今日の競売について 聞いてみたが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:32.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You knew my strategy was a dead end. Yes. Why did you need to think \Nbefore making your move?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:34.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}コミュニティーの回答は まだだそうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:34.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You could have made that move at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:38.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「旅団」が みんな生きてるってことも 教えてやればいいじゃねえか。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:38.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The King has moved this match off the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:40.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうすりゃ マフィアも考え直すだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:40.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A wrong answer could mean
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:43.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いや　結果は　恐らく同じだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:43.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:47.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}コミュニティーは　流星街との摩擦を 懸念しているからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:47.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your "remote concealment" strategy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:51.36,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「旅団」への攻撃は 完全に終結したとみていいだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:51.36,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}is actually named "kokoriko."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:56.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうか…。 だが　私が本当に知りたいのは そこじゃ　ない。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:56.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I came up with that strategy... ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:11:00.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}競売が　予定通り行われるか どうかの一点だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:11:00.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Placing the lieutenant general in the center
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:07.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前　まさか　迎え撃つ気か？ そりゃ　いくら何でも無謀だぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:07.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to counter a three-pronged attack is also a\N move I devised, called "general in the middle."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:10.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうやって　マフィアの援護なしに 戦うつもりだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:10.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}At the time, both drew a lot of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:13.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それは誤解だよ　レオリオ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:13.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Moving from kokoriko to general in the middle \Nwas a popular transition that tested
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:18.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}奴らの後ろ盾など 最初からない。 あっ　あ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:18.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}both players' ability to read their opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:21.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカ！　俺達にも 何か手伝わせてよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:21.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was pretty happy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:26.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何でもいい　どんなことでもやる！ 断れ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:26.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}that a fool like me could figure \Nout a smart strategy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:30.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}賞金は撤回されたんだぞ？ 分かってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:30.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But then, I saw how to defeat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:43.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「旅団」を止めたい その気持は変わってないよ。 断れ　断れ 命懸けだぞ。 おいおい　火に油だっつうの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:43.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A year after I came up with kokoriko, an opponent used it against me \Nin the national tournament, and I figured out how to counter it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:50.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よし　打ち合わせをしよう。 うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:50.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I won the match, but the strategy disappeared from \Nofficial matches and textbooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:51.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やるんかい！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:51.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That the Supreme Leader thought \Nof the same strategy as I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:12:03.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まず　奴らのアジトを張る役 中継係が１人。 俺が　やるよ。 ターゲットは パクノダという女のみ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:12:03.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was so honored, and touched...\NMy heart trembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:05.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それ以外は　無視していい。 ＯＫ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:05.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It felt like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:13.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}大丈夫　無理はしない。 私と共に行動する　運転手が１人。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:13.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Like seeing my child brought back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:16.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}レオリオ　頼めるか？ えっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:16.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That was how it felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:24.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おっ　おう…。 平気だよ　クラピカのそばなら 安全だから。 おい　キルア！ まるで　俺がビビって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:24.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So it was difficult for me \Nto take that life again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:27.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一瞬　間が空いたみたいな とり方すんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:27.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That was why
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:28.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカ　俺は？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:28.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I hesitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:38.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}また　奴らと直接 対峙しなきゃなんないじゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:38.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:40.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それは　やり方次第だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:40.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:43.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やり方？　どんな作戦だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:43.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:50.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}敵が　ゴンに 気をとられている隙に 私がパクノダを捕らえ 車で連れ去る。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:50.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once we begin again, you won't get any more breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:52.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何だよ　そのアバウトな作戦。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:52.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:57.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}不確定要素が多過ぎて　これ以上 細かな作戦は立てられない。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:57.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:05.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}方法は　ゴンに任せるが 最低０．５秒　できれば１秒 相手の注意を引きつけてほしい。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:05.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I believe this is the first time the King has ever listened \Nto anyone speak for such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:08.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１秒…　だね。 ああ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:08.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, it should have no significance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:16.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}できるだろうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:16.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Four hours have passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:20.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴン　お前がカギだ　できそうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:20.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He got bored and started reading...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:24.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まだ分からない　考えてみるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:24.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That guy's too easy to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:30.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もしも　競売が予定通りなら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:30.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, you're ready to start? Has it already been five hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:33.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それまでに「クモ」は　必ず動く。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:33.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wait, it's only half full.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:43.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もちろん 私のリスクが増したからだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:43.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You just noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:46.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}早急にパクノダを 始末せねばならない。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:46.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We aren't starting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:50.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何を犠牲にしてもだ。 こいつ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:50.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's already over. Look at your ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:55.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカに感じた 威圧感の正体は　これか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:55.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A rope of smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:57.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}前以上の覚悟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:57.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That took a lot of effort...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:05.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカ 俺にも「念」の刃を刺してよ。 「『念』の刃を」って…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:05.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I had to go all the way around \Nso you wouldn't notice, so it turned into quite a long rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:10.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴン　話　聞いてたか？ クラピカは　「旅団」以外の人間を 攻撃したら　死ぬんだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:10.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In any case, all that's left \Nis to wind up the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:18.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}声が　デカい！ だったらさ　何でクラピカの胸には 「念」の刃が刺さってんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:18.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now it's only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:21.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカは 「旅団」の人間じゃないでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:21.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your turn to try whatever you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:28.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ここからの話は　さらに 私のリスクを上げることになる。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:28.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But it won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:32.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ＯＫ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:32.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You should take the smoke seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おい　キルア。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Essentially, it's a rope that can't be severed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:52.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}結論から言おう それは　確かに可能だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:52.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I knew it... He won't attack me because \Nthis is a game of tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:15:03.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}５つの鎖には　それぞれ 違う能力が宿っている。 その中で 「クモ」攻撃用の鎖は２つ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:15:03.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If I touch his body, it will break his ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:05.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１つは「チェーンジェイル」。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:05.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He has no patience, but he chose \Nfor the game to last eight hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:09.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}捕らえた者を強制的に 「絶」の状態にして拘束する。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:09.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm not the one you're putting pressure on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:12.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「クモ」を捕らえるための能力だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:12.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The pressure's on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:22.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そして　これが 「ジャッジメントチェーン」。 標的の心臓に　この刃を刺して ルールを宣言し
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:22.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Cheetu's power was still a work in progress. With his back against the wall, \Ndesperate for a way out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:27.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}順守させる。 そのルールを破れば　死。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:27.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He created a new ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最初は　単純に
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A crossbow and claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:43.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「『クモ』でない者を 鎖で攻撃すれば死ぬ」 …というルールを考え 自分に刃を打とうとした。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:43.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He can fight at any range.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:46.38,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　その時　ふと思った。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:46.38,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Thanks! You helped me gain an awesome new power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:50.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私自身への攻撃も そのルールの範疇だったら？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:50.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey, do you know what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:58.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私だけは 例外になるのかもしれないが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:58.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You sure you want to come closer?! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:01.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}確実に そうだと言える自信は　なかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:01.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm quite sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:08.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そこで　ルールを限定した。 「チェーンジェイル」での攻撃は 「クモ」にしか使わない。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:08.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why would you want a power \Nthat's slower than you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:13.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}従って　「ジャッジメントチェーン」は 「クモ」以外にも使える。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:13.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Ah. Why don't you try those claws?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:19.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ただし　使用条件がある。 使用条件？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:19.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then I won't have to walk over. I'll tell you why you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:24.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この鎖は 緋の眼の時にしか使えない。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:24.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's because you're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:38.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}中指の能力は 手元から離さないことと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:38.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Die! Then you can never touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:41.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}死というリスクを背負うことで クリアした。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:41.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This sensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:46.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}小指のほうは 私の特異体質が解決してくれた。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:46.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It can't be... Smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:50.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}緋の眼が現れた時 私は　特質系となり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:50.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.81,0:16:52.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}覚えた能力であれば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.81,0:16:52.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:56.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１００％の精度　威力で 使用できる。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:56.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wh-When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:05.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よく　分かんないけど つまり　「念」の刃は 俺にも刺せるってことだよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:05.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}While you were reading manga \Nand laughing like a fool, I created a copy of myself from smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:07.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:07.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And I covered myself with smoke \Nthat looked like grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:11.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いいよ　ルールは任せる。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:11.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My copy went one way, and I went the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:19.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前の覚悟　確かに受け取った。 その刃ってさ　３本　出せる？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:19.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The fight continues, even while one sleeps. You shouldn't have looked away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:23.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}任務完了の後は そのルール　解除できるんだろうな？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:23.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Looks like we're back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:25.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルア　レオリオ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:25.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, do you still want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:29.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こっちも　２人で話したんだが やっぱり　参加するからには…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:29.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:31.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一連托生っしょ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:31.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's a wise decision...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:33.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}答えは？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:33.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then why not tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:38.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}両方とも可能だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:38.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}what would have happened \Nif I hadn't caught you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:42.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　３人とも １つ勘違いしている。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:42.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There's no point in asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:45.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私は　お前達に刃を刺す気など
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:45.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once I've been caught, \NI can't use that power anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:48.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}初めから　全くないのだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:48.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That was the condition I set.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:52.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だったら 何で　リスクが増すだけなのに こんな話を…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:52.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Really? I feel bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:56.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴン　お前の… いや　お前達の覚悟に対する
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:56.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's no big deal. I'll ask Shaia-sama for a new power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:58.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私なりの礼だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:58.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Next time, I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:02.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}仮に　お前達から 秘密が漏れたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:02.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You'd better be ready! His superior
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:05.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私は　もう　何ひとつ後悔しない。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:05.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}is most likely a Royal Guard named Shaia, who has the power to release Nen skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:12.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私は　いい仲間を持った。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:12.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So if the selection is carried out, \Nwinning will become very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ずるいよ　クラピカ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Gon and Killua made the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:23.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そんなこと言われたら 命　懸けるより
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:23.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We need to meet. Let's talk inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:26.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よっぽど　プレッシャーに なっちゃうよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:26.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Reinforcements have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:28.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それが　狙いだからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:28.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's a crayfish and a wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:33.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なんだ　そうか　アハハ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:33.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Are they strong? If I knew, my job would be easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:37.37,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フフフフ…。 笑えねえぞ　おい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:37.37,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Right now, they're trying to gauge our strength. So it's currently a stalemate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:41.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おっ　さて… んじゃ　俺　行くよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:41.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Our goal is to buy time, so it all works out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}時間が　もったいないからね。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I suspect it's because I took out this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:49.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルア　気をつけてね。 おう　任しとけって。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:49.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Those dragonflies were acting \Nas security cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:43.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それじゃあ　班を決める。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:43.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}borrow an ability in exchange \Nfor granting the target a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:49.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}来週は　この班を基本に動き 単独行動は　絶対に避けること。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:49.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}However, two conditions must be met.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:53.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}シズク　パクノダ　マチ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:53.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}First, he must have seen the ability or know its name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:57.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}コルトピ　フィンクス　フェイタン。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:57.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Second, he must grant a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:20:05.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ノブナガとシャルナークは　俺と。 ボノレノフ　フランクリン ヒソカは　ここで待機。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:20:05.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}After confirming that his favor is not \Nfree and is expected to be repaid, this skill will activate, assuming \Nthe target agrees to his conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:14.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}団長　１つ　いい？ 子供がさ ここの場所　知ってんだけど。 子供？ まぁ　鎖野郎とは 関係ないみたいなんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:14.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Got it! Once all conditions are met, Leol's \Ndispenser automatically stores data, which can be checked at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:22.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やっぱり　どうも　気になるのよね。 そうだ　忘れてたぜ！ 団長　そいつの入団　推薦するぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:22.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}However, if the target dies, \Nthe data will be deleted. Flutter's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:26.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ちょっと… こっちは　そんなつもりで 話をしてんじゃないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:26.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I believe there's been no communication
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}話してくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}because he's unconscious or far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:34.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なるほど 確かに面白そうな奴ではある。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:34.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A rental can be used for one hour. During the rental period, the target \Ncannot use the borrowed power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:39.36,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}が　話を聞く限り　そいつは 「クモ」には　入らないだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:39.36,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Anyway, Flutter is still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:42.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}説得するさ！ とにかく　一度　見てくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:42.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Looks like we'll be able to stay in touch. Once Flutter's Satellite Dragonflies
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:45.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}団長　ダメだよ 乗せられちゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:45.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}verify the location of the suit \Nwith the glasses, we'll start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:51.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}で　マチ お前が　気になることとは？ え？　あ　何となく。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:51.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So we keep the small fry at a distance \Nwhile you take on the suit with the glasses. You gonna be okay on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:58.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}勘か？ お前の勘は　頼りになるからな。 その子供　もしかしたら　何か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:58.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Just trust me. I wouldn't give \Nyou a job you can't handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:21:01.38,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}重大な　つながりが あるかもしれない。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:21:01.38,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And I don't want you to see my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:05.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}用心のため　アジトのダミーを 増やしておくか。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:05.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll do whatever it takes to \Ncomplete this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}コルトピ　あと１０棟　行けるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.29,0:21:14.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}５０は平気。 それと　偽のアジトに 誰かが侵入すれば　すぐ分かるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.29,0:21:14.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can't afford to wait around here. Not until the King is in my debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:18.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}僕のコピー 「円」の役割も果たすから。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:18.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When Leol takes the dispensed IOU and \Ntears it up, the effect activates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.29,0:21:28.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何かが違う…　場所？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.29,0:21:28.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Time to start scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:33.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ　まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:33.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:37.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アジトの建物が増えてる！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:37.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is upsetting. During our matches, I am the only \None who's getting flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:47.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}降りしきる雨の中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:47.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I would have expected this to be \Nhumiliating on a new level. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.29,0:21:50.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}パクノダを捕らえる作戦が 始まった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.29,0:21:50.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}At the same time, I am enjoying our matches.
